added: Both primaries took place on August 18, 2020.<ref>{{Cite web|url=https://www.elections.alaska.gov/Core/electioncalendar.php|title=Alaska Division of Elections|website=www.elections.alaska.gov}}</ref> The election was impacted by the revelation of recordings related to the controversial [[Pebble Mine]] project, which could adversely impact the ecosystem of [[Bristol Bay]].
